    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 requirements per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. The CFD model is accepted for the stated COU of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Physical fault conditions encountered during extended in vivo bypass use (bearing wear, motor voltage transients, sensor drift) are acknowledged in the COU description; fault tolerance documentation is referenced as existing separately, and this gap does not affect the nominal-condition credibility determination recorded here.",
